    <h4>Associates</h4>
    <p>Associates are respected individuals who support Dot-Public’s aims and are publicly
        affiliated with the project but are not required to undertake regular work. They lend
        legitimacy, visibility, and influence through their association. Associates may be consulted
        occasionally or invited to public events, but their involvement is light-touch by default.</p>

    <p>An Associate:</p>
    <ul>
